      "id": "intermediate-2026-06-24",
      "levelGroup": "intermediate",
      "title": "Resetting Focus During the Day",
      "cefrLevel": "B1",
      "summaryJa": "日中の集中力をリセットする工夫を扱います。",
      "sourceUrls": [
        "https://www.cdc.gov/workplacehealthpromotion/index.html"
